<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong><img src="/media/13051208/voucher-fan.png" alt="Voucher -fan" width="174" height="151" align="left" />WIN £500 worth of holiday vouchers*</strong> by completing our <strong>Guest Feedback Form</strong> for<a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/2525420/Inghams-Chalet-Hotel-Guest-Feedback-2015-16" target="_blank" title="Chalet Hotel GFF 15/16"> </a><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/2652082/Inghams-Chalet-Guest-Feedback-2015-16" target="_blank" title="Chalet GFF 15/16">Chalet</a> &amp; <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/2525420/Inghams-Chalet-Hotel-Guest-Feedback-2015-16" target="_blank" title="Chalet Hotel GFF 15/16">Chalet Hotels</a>.</p>
<p>The feedback you provide will help us to improve our service and our programme in future seasons, and as a way of saying thank you, all completed forms will be entered into our prize draw to <strong>WIN £500 worth of holiday vouchers</strong>.</p>
<p>Please ensure we have your name and address to be eligible to enter.</p>
<br /><br />
<div class="data-grid" style="float: left;"><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/2525420/Inghams-Chalet-Hotel-Guest-Feedback-2015-16" target="_blank" title="Chalet Hotel GFF Link"><img src="/media/13051193/chalet-hotel-cta.png" alt="CTA" width="287" height="47" rel="287,47" /></a></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: right;"><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/s3/2652082/Inghams-Chalet-Guest-Feedback-2015-16" target="_blank" title="Chalet GFF Link"><img src="/media/13051192/chalet-cta.png" alt="CTA" width="287" height="47" rel="287,47" /></a></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<br />
<p><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Prize Draw Terms &amp; Conditions</span></em><br /><br /><em>* Prize draw eligibility open to UK and Ireland residents over 18 who have completed this Guest Feedback survey, including name and address. This promotion is not available to employees of Hotelplan Ltd or affiliate companies. The prize draw will take place on the 1st June 2016, using all entries received by 1st May 2016 and the winner will be advised in writing. The name of the winner will be available from us on request. The £500 holiday voucher is valid for 1 year and can be redeemed on any brochured Inghams holiday. Holidays are subject to terms and conditions. Please see relevant brochures.</em><br /><br /><em>We use our Guest Feedback forms to monitor and improve our service levels throughout the company but are unable to reply to comments made here. If you would like a personal reply, please write separately within 21 days to Inghams, Mountain House, Station Road, Godalming, Surrey, GU7 1EX or email <a href="mailto:guest.services@inghams.co.uk">guest.services@inghams.co.uk</a>. Unless you advise us in writing not to do so, comments made on this Guest Feedback from may be used in future brochures or marketing material.</em></p>
</div>
